  "contents": "<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/core\", \"name\": \"@angular/core\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/core/input\", \"name\": \"input\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a> > <a href=\"api/core\">@angular/core</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/packages/core/src/authoring/input/input.ts#L103-L108\" aria-label=\"查看源码\" title=\"查看源码\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"input\">input<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/input#input\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label const\">const</label>\n    <label class=\"api-status-label dev-preview\" title=\"此 API 仅供开发者预览\">\n      <a href=\"guide/releases#developer-preview\">开发者预览</a>\n    </label>\n    \n  </header>\n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n  <section class=\"short-description\">\n    <p>The <code>input</code> function allows declaration of inputs in directives and\ncomponents.</p>\n\n    <p><a href=\"api/core/input#description\">查看更多...</a></p>\n  </section>\n  <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">\n  const input: <a href=\"api/core/InputFunction\" class=\"code-anchor\">InputFunction</a>;\n  </code-example>\n\n  \n<section class=\"description\">\n  <h2 id=\"description\">说明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/input#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p>Initializes an input with an initial value. If no explicit value\nis specified, Angular will use <code>undefined</code>.</p>\n<p>Consider using <code>input.required</code> for inputs that don't need an\ninitial value.</p>\n  <p>Further information is available in the <a href=\"api/core/input#usage-notes\">Usage Notes...</a></p>\n</section>\n\n<section class=\"usage-notes\">\n  <h2 id=\"usage-notes\">使用说明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/input#usage-notes\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p>Initialize an input in your directive or component by declaring a\nclass field and initializing it with the <code>input()</code> function.</p>\n<code-example language=\"ts\">\n@<a href=\"api/core/Directive\" class=\"code-anchor\">Directive</a>({..})\nexport class MyDir {\n  firstName = input&#x3C;string>();            // string|undefined\n  lastName = input.required&#x3C;string>();    // string\n  age = input(0);                         // number\n}\n</code-example>\n\n</section></div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/core\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/core\n - api/core/Directive\n - api/core/InputFunction\n - api/core/input#description\n - api/core/input#input\n - api/core/input#usage-notes\n - guide/releases#developer-preview\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/packages/core/src/authoring/input/input.ts#L103-L108\n-->"
}